{"word":"σήμερον","slug":"σήμερον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>σήμερον</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ IE\">IE</a>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <b>today <a href='B:470 6:11'>Mt 6:11</a>, <a href='B:470 6:30'>30</a>; <a href='B:470 11:23'>11:23</a>; <a href='B:470 27:19'>27:19</a>; <a href='B:480 14:30'>Mk 14:30</a>; <a href='B:490 2:11'>Lk 2:11</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in Lk, <b><a href='B:510 4:9'>Ac 4:9</a>; <a href='B:510 27:33'>27:33</a>; <a href='B:540 3:14'>2 Cor 3:14f</a>; <a href='B:650 3:13'>Hb 3:13</a>; <a href='B:650 13:8'>13:8</a>; <a href='B:660 4:13'>Js 4:13</a>.</b> W. emphasis in the phrase <el>ἡ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σήμερον\">σήμερον</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἡμέρα\">ἡμέρα</a></el> this very day <b><a href='B:470 28:15'>Mt 28:15</a>; <a href='B:510 20:26'>Ac 20:26</a>; <a href='B:520 11:8'>Ro 11:8</a>.</b> In a collective phrase expressing a short time <b><a href='B:490 13:32'>Lk 13:32f</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:σημειόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:σημικίνθιον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}